Kar gay, kuŋ gee kuuk Buŋ doɓtu, kuŋ gee kuuk *cawar ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi ho ku elgiyo, isguwoŋ ziŋkiko ar ziŋkiko ku maaniiko, iŋ neenduwko taat samaane, iŋ niyin taat taɓ, taat un̰je ka ziŋkiko, taat dalullay, ho iŋ taaɓin taat taɓ.
