Ka seener, Buŋ, ŋaar kaak jilinte, ŋaar sellen̰ ho ŋa elgiite ɗo geemir.
Kar gay, ŋaar jilintiɗo. Ŋaar bal nige maan kaak samaane ni gintu ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi. Kar gay, ŋa elgiite. Ŋa jilinti iŋ gudurre ta Ruwwin ta Buŋdi taat nam ni weeyig marbinto ho iŋ marbinto taat marbinto asaan taɓ.
Buŋ berteŋ gamin dakina ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi iŋ siŋ ku Iisa Masi gay jilinte.
Ŋa gintu pa-ak a paa kat, gii gase botol taat Buŋ yaate berin barkin ta Buŋdi ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi. Paa kat, gii ice kaawoy a gii gase goye ka gaasɗo ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi.
Kaaw-at ka seener. Ɗo gamin-aŋ ko, naan̰ kaawin seen di ho ki raka naan̰ kaawin seen di. Ansii kat, gee kuuk aamin ɗo Buŋdi, ŋuu obin riy taat samaane di, paa kat, ŋuu gine samaane ɗo uŋco ka geemir. Gamin ŋuur-aŋ samaane ho ŋuu nige maan portiko ɗo uŋco ka geemir.
Ya ku talaag gamin-aŋku, ku poocgit kaawinco ku meen̰co, ku poocgit biŋkico iŋ biŋkico di, ku poocgit seene, ku poocgit seene. Ku ibanno maanna-aŋka, asaan ŋu ibanno maanna.
Ŋaar-ak ko, ya gem looga iŋ kaaw rakki di, ŋa ooyiita. Ka seeriŋkar oki, ŋa ooyiita.
Min ŋa taltu kadar gem-aŋ ƴiimit wijeeney ho ŋa newsiig nigin̰ji-ak, koɗok di, Buŋ ɗiyiiji daŋaayne.
Ya nu n̰aamaag Artemis ɗo werin̰ Tisik, gaay koɗok di kii ɓaa talin̰ annere ɗo geeger ka Nikopoolis, asaan ɗo wer-ak ko, ki goyiy margina. "
Ɗo wer-ak, nu kaawiico ɗo agindaw ku gaanuundi iŋ gee ku pey a ŋuuco kaawe dakina dakina. Nu kaawiico pa-ak a paa kat, yoo maan ka gaanuundi sa, ŋuu rasin̰coɗo.
Ŋu eeltu menaw ŋuur-ak di ho ɗo menaw ŋuur-ak, ŋu pooc icin̰ gamin kuuk samaane ŋu giniy gamin kuuk samaane. Ŋu rakaaɗo peyin̰ gamin-ak iŋ gamin kuuk samaane kuuk yaako nece ɗo gamin ku duniiner. Yampa, ziŋkico sa, pa ŋuu nige ziŋkicoɗo.
Gee okin̰co yaan̰ ozile sawa iŋ nunu. Ho ŋuur kuuk elgiini sa, obguwaani imaanco. Buŋ yaako goye iŋ kuŋko okin̰co. Ampa-ak, Buŋ yaako goye iŋ kuŋko okin̰co. "
