ho ŋaa jilin̰ gee kuuk asa min ɗo duniiner. Ŋuur-ak, kolaw ku muut-ak ko, ansii ko, ŋu goy ɗo ɓerrin kuuk as ɗo ɓerrinco.
Sando, ka seener gay, ŋa bal obin̰ *ɗubal ku Buŋdi ɗo werti, kar gay, ŋa obin̰ ja min tamba ta Ibraayim.
