Iisa gaaytu pey ɗo kaawoy aman: " Dakoŋ bomboŋ diyenno kaƴko ar *Seetanne geciyko, ƴiriy taat ŋu geciig Buŋ ɗo goosiner, ƴiriy taat ŋa geciig *Seetanne gecaako.
