Ŋa un̰jitu ɗo wer ka Buŋdi-aka. Ŋa bal un̰je misa iŋ baar ku ammaamnar, wala iŋ kan̰ ɗurkilnal, wala iŋ baar ku ammaamnar. Paa ko, Iisa un̰jitu pey ɗo wer kaak *cawar aale ho ŋa gastu jile ka gaasɗo.
Ka seener gay, baar ku baarir, ku pooɗ iŋ kuuk ŋu ɗuunit maasoy ho iŋ baar kuuk ŋu ɗuunit maasoy-ak, kuuk gaara kadar ŋuur kuuk goy ziŋkico sellen̰ ar ziŋkico kaak samaanno ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi. Iŋ taar-at kat, kuu gine *cawar ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi, kuu gine *cawar ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi.
Min ŋaar-ak, ba aaro, baar ku Masi-ak yaa gine maman? Ŋaar meen̰ji satkine. Ŋaar meen̰ji satkine ɗo Buŋdi iŋ Ruwwin ta Buŋdi taat gaasga. Paa kat, baar ku Masi-ak yaa saamiye aditko min ɗo gamin kuuk samaanno kuuk min ɗo muuti. Paa kat, nii gine riy ta Buŋ kaak goy mento ho kuu abdiye Buŋ kaak goy mento.
Ɗo saan taar-at ko, Iisa Masi gin *Mee satkiner ɗo *Jamaw ta marbinto. Ansii kat, gee kuuk Buŋ doɓtu asa mate a ŋuu gase jile min ɗo zunuubinnar kuuk ŋu gintu ɗo uŋji ka awalle. Paa kat, ŋuur kuuk Buŋ koliigu yaa gase pey haginey taat ŋa kaawiico a ŋuu gase goye ka gaasɗo ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi.
Cokiyoŋ gay, ɗo wer kaak gin *gaanuun mattu, ya gem-ak mat ko, ŋaar isgigɗo ya ŋa gaasit kaaw taat ŋu siirtu.
Ka seener gay, ya gem kaak obit kaaw-at, taar yaa mate. Kar ya gem kaak obit kaaw-at, taar yaa gine tak-tak wiktin taat ŋa goyiy mento.
Kar Iisa kaawtu pey aman: " Ya awalle gay, gii barkiyin̰ baar ku baarir oki, Buŋ toɗcoɗo.
Ɗo bi ka *gaanuun ka Muusa kaawtu okin̰ji, ŋa kaawtu pa-ak asaan ŋa kaawco ɗo geemir kadar *gaanuun okin̰ji kaak Buŋ kaawtu ɗo *gaanuun ka Muusa. Min ŋa kaawtu pa-ak, ŋa ictu baar, ŋa ɗuuniig iŋ amay iŋ amay ho ŋa ɗuuniig iŋ ɗuuney, kar ŋa ɗuuniig ziŋkico ɗo maktumner-ata. Min ŋu doriit kaaw-at di, ŋa kockiciitit ɗo gee okin̰co kuuk goy ɗo wer-aka,
ho ŋa ɗiytu aman: " Ŋuur-aŋ baar-aŋ ɗuunit *Jamaw ta marbinto taat Buŋ kaawiiko a ŋuu gine.
Paa ko, ŋa ɗukumiico pey baarco ar baar ku *ger ka Buŋdi ho iŋ gamin okin̰co kuuk ŋu gina riy ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi oki.
Kar gamin okin̰co kuuk iŋ baar sa, *gaanuunte kaawa a ŋuu goye *cawar ay maanna min ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi. Kar ya baar bal *cawar aale, Buŋ saamiyaajiɗo zunuubinna yoo wer kaak ŋu gaasɗo baar ku hadinner. "
Ka seener gay, Buŋ kaawco kaawa a gamin kuuk gaara gamin kuuk goy kuwa ka samaaner di gin ko *cawar a ŋuu gine *cawar. Kar gay, ŋuur kuuk goy kuwa ka samaaner gay, ŋuur-ak di iciy paa di. Iŋ taar-an ko, ŋu giniy gamin kuuk ŋu giniy satkine.
Ka seener gay, Masi kaak Buŋ doɓtu-ak, ŋaar bal un̰je ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi, ŋaar geen̰ji di ar maan kaak taɓ kaak gee rakiy a ŋuu gine. Ŋaar meen̰ji di un̰je ka samaaner di. Diŋ gay, ŋaar as ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi uŋci, nii talin̰ji ko ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi di.
Ŋaar gay bal gine ziy ar meen̰ji diirin̰ji. Sando, mee satkiner ka tatko un̰jitu atta ɗo ger ka Buŋdi ka tatko iŋ meen̰ji di iŋ baar ku gem kaak ka pey. Ampaa ko, ŋa un̰jitu atta iŋ baar ku gem kaak ŋu ibingiga.
Min Buŋ kilgiyit duniine kilgiyit duniine, Iisa Masi taltu kadar ŋaa taaɓiyen̰ ja dakina min ŋa kilgiyit duniine. Kar gay, ɗo wiktin taat duniin gaaye, Buŋ gaayaag gem-ak a ŋaa gine saamiye ka zunuubinnico, asaan ŋaar isgigɗo tak-tak iŋ satkine. "
Ta taar-at ko, gee liya ko muutco rakki di, ŋuu mate, kar ba aar gay, seriin ta Buŋdi asiy ɗukume seriine.
Ansii ko, Iisa Masi oki, ŋaar mat ko rakki di ŋaa icin zunuubinna ku gee dakina a ŋaa minin̰co. Kar ka seeriŋkar gay, ŋa asa bayne ziy ka seeriŋkar, bal zunuubinna, ɗo ŋuur kuuk ŋa doɓtu a ŋuu gase jile.
Ka seener gay, gaanuun kaak Buŋ kaawtu-ak, ŋaar goy ko gondiko ɗo gamin kuuk samaane kuuk yaa ase. Kar gay, ŋaar goyɗo serek di iŋ gamin kuuk goy ɗo duniiner. Ka seener gay, gamin kuuk ŋu giniy satkine ar ŋuur-aŋku. Paa ko, gamin kuuk ŋu giniy satkine-ak ginno pey botol taat ŋuu gine *cawar ɗo uŋco ka geemir.
Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, wiktin taat ŋu giniy *satkin-at ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi, ŋu bal peyin̰ pey asaan satkinco-at wadirtu. Sando, ŋuur kuuk aaɗaat satkin-at sa, ziŋkico gingigɗo pey asaan ŋu gina jookumo.
Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, koɗok di, gee liya maan kaak ŋu saamiyiig zunuubinnico rakki di.
Ka seener gay, baar ku ammaamnar iŋ *geme ku pooɗar, ŋuur saamiyaagɗo zunuubinna min ɗo uŋco ka geemir.
Wiktin taat Iisa asiy duniine, ŋa kaawtu ɗo Kitamner aman: ‟ Nu rakaaɗo satkine ho *satkin taat ŋu giniyɗo. Kar gay, nu rakaaɗo zir, nu rakaaɗo satkine.
Ɗo bi ka zunuubinnar, kiŋ meen̰ji sa balco cigile yoo zunuubinna.
Hiyya, nu kaawtu aman: " Di ŋaar-ak, nun as ko ɗo Kitamner a naa gine riy taat Buŋ rakiyo. Ɗo bi kanto ko, ŋu siir ɗo bi kanto a naa gine taat ki rakiyo. "
Min ŋa kaawtu pey aman: ‟ *satkin kuuk ŋu giniy *satkin ɗo Buŋdi, ŋuur kuuk ŋu giniy satkine, kuuk ŋu bertu *satkin ɗo Buŋdi ho kuuk ŋu giniy satkine ɗo bi ka zunuubinnar, ki bal ooye ho ki bal ooye. " Sando, ki bal ooye ho ki bal ooye.
ho ŋa kaawiiji aman: " An ko taat ki rakiyo. An di kaak ki rakiyo. Ŋa ɗukumig kaak awalle-aŋka, ŋaa rawte kaawoy, kar ŋaa gasin̰ ka seeriŋkar. "
Buŋ ginit riy taar-at ko iŋ taat Buŋ raktu a ŋuu gine sellen̰ ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi iŋ *satkin taat ŋu beriig zi ka Iisa Masi doo.
Kun kawta, gay satkiner rakki pey goya. Ŋa gina riy ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi ho ŋa giniy satkine. Satkin-ak gay, ŋu giniy satkine dakin aale ho satkin-ak gay gedarro imilin̰ zunuubinna tak-tak.
Ɗo wiktin taar-at, Iisa Masi gay ber *satkin rakki ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi a ŋaa gine satkine, kar ŋa goytu ɗo meeday ta Buŋdi. Sando, satkin-at gay, ŋa gin *satkin rakki ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi ɗo bi ka zunuubinnar.
Kar ba aaro, ŋa ɓaa ere nam wiktin taat ŋuuco gedire ɗo adiney, ŋuu gine wer ka lee asin̰ji.
Ka seener gay, taar kat ta neginda a ŋaaco peyin̰ gurusco ɗo gee kuuk Buŋ doɓtu ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi.
Ruwwin ta Buŋdi sa gaaraako pey kadar maanna-ak kaawaako seene, asaan ta taar ko kaawa pey aman:
An ko *gaanuun taat naa amile iŋ ŋuura min ɗo menaw ŋuur-ak, tamba ta Buŋdi aman: ‟ An ko kaaw taat naaco gaare iŋ ŋuura. Naa un̰jin̰ gaanuun-ak ɗo aditco ho naa siirin̰ji ɗo kaƴco. "
Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, nu imilaagɗo pey zunuubinnico iŋ zunuubinnico okin̰co kuuk samaanno ŋu giniyo. " "
Kar ɗo wer kaak Buŋ saamiyiy zunuubinna-aŋ, ŋu gina pey *satkin taat ŋuu gine pey zunuubinna.
Ampa-ak, gem kol siŋtay, kaawkoŋ bombo, iŋ baar ku Iisa Masi, gee kuuk Buŋ doɓtu yaa gase gudurre taat ŋuuco gedire.
Ŋa gaarinti botol taat taɓ a nii gase goye ka gaasɗo. Taar-an gay, ta siŋji ka Iisa Masi.
Ɗo wer-ak, ŋa gin gay satkiner dakina kaak gooƴa ger ka Buŋdi.
Di ŋaar-ak, gi ɓaa sawa iŋ gelbin kaak taɓ ɗo imaanji ho iŋ gelbin kaak taɓ ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi. Gamin gii icin̰ gelbinte min ɗo aditco taat samaanno ho ziŋkini ŋu acciig iŋ amay kuuk *cawar.
Min ni kaaw a ni raka goye ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi-ak, illa gii rasin imaan taat ni gintu, asaan ŋaar kaak kaawiite a gii aamine ɗo Buŋdi.
Ya gi goyiy misa iŋ gelbin rakki, gi ɓaa gine ziŋkico taat gii elguwe ho gii gine gamin kuuk samaane.
Ya ku ɓaawaw ɗo geray ku salaaner, dakoŋ rasenno ziŋkiko ar ku gee ku salaaner ku Yuudinnar. Illa indoŋ Buŋ a ŋaaco gaaye. Ka seener gay, maan kaak ku taliy-aŋ asa ko moota iŋ ƴiriy ta Buŋdi.
Ka seener gay, min gi gaarig ko zunuubinni ho min diŋ gay, ni gastu botol ta seen ta Buŋdi, ho diŋ gay, gi ginno pey satkine taat ŋuu ginin̰ pey ɗo bi ka zunuubinnico.
Ŋaar-ak kolaw yaa ase ɗo uŋco ka geemir a ŋuuco ɗukume seriine. Ɗo saan taar-at ko, gee kuuk ƴilaaɗo Buŋ yaaco taaɓiye aale ho taaɓin yaa ozilin̰ ŋuur kuuk yaa ase ɗo uŋco ka geemir.
Ŋa poociit gaanuun ka Muusa: " Ya ŋu bal deen kaƴa iŋ biŋkico di, kaaw-at mat ko, illa ya saadinna seer wal subba di, ŋuu deen̰ji. "
Ku pakira maa di kadar nun Roŋ ka Buŋdi, nu poocga! Ku ibanno baati kadar nu Roŋ ka Buŋdi, ŋuur-ak nec taaɓiye arro. Ku ibanno pey baar ku *Jamaw ta marbinto taat Buŋ asiikonno iŋ kuŋko. Ku ibinno baati ampa. Kar ku gastu pey baar ku Buŋdi ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi. Kar Ruwwin ta barkin ta Buŋdi kat n̰aamig iŋ gudurre ta Buŋdi.
Asaan ni iban kaaw taat ŋa kaawtu aman: ‟ Ya ƴiriy rakki, nun meendu naaco ɗukume seriine, nun meendu sa, naa kappiyinti. " Ni iban kaaw taat ŋa kaawtu aman: " Rabbin Buŋ yaa ɗukume seriine ɗo geen̰ji. "
Ŋaar Buŋ kaak goy mento, illa ŋaa gine kolaw ɗo pisin̰ji ka Buŋ kaak goy mento.
Moyoŋ ɗo gamin kuuk awalle kuuk goy anne. Ɗo wiktin taar-at ko, ku gastu portikaw dakina, kar ku taaɓiy dakina nam ku taaɓiy paa di.
Ɗo wiktin taar-at, ŋu iciig gee kuuk aale ho ŋu taaɓiyiigu ɗo uŋco ka geemir. Kar daarin̰ gay, ŋu maaɗiy sawa iŋ gee kuuk gina riy taar-an di.
Asaan ku taaɓiyco samaane ɗo gee kuuk goy ɗo daŋaayner ho ya ŋu sokig ku maaniiko ŋu sokig loko-ak, ooyon̰co iŋ galal, asaan ku iban kadar maaniikoŋ sa goy ko ɗo pisin̰co di.
Dakoŋ rasenno gurusko taat ku dummiyiy ziŋkiko. Gamin ŋaar-ak, Buŋ yaako kappiyin hagin ta gamin okin̰co.
Goyoŋ bombo, zeeɗoŋ ɗo imaanko, asaan ya ku ginit riy ta Buŋdi taat Buŋ rakiyo, kuu gasin̰ maan kaak ŋa kaawtu a ŋaaji bere.
Asaan ɗo wiktin taat Buŋ yaa ase-ak, ŋaar yaa ase koɗok di, ŋa asa gaaye tak-tak.
Kar ŋaar kaak sellen̰ ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi-ak gay, ŋaar yaa gase iŋ imaanco, kar ŋaa goye. Ya ŋa bal obin̰ji gay, nu rawtaagɗo tak-tak. "
Kar gay, ya ni raka gine paliinna-ak, ansi-ak, maan kaak ni gintu yaa nige maanna. Kar gay, maan kaak ni gintu pa-ak, ŋaar aamine ɗo Iisa Masi a ŋaa jilin̰ gee kuuk goy ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi.
Kar imaan gay, taar ko maan kaak gi hariye ɗo gamin kuuk gi hariyiy a gi goye. Gamin gay, ŋaar-ak ɗo bi ka gamin kuuk gi talgigɗo misa gamin kuuk gi talgigɗo.
Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, agindaw ku darrer kaawtu a taaco kaawe.
Ampa-ak, ni pakira kadar kaawoy ta Buŋdi, taar goy doo, nii obin̰ iŋ imaanco. Ni ooyɗo gamin kuuk gee taliigɗo min ɗo gamin kuuk ni gintu, kar gay, ni ibanno gamin kuuk ni gintu.
Ɗo bi ka *Kayin ko, Abeel bertu *satkin taat samaane ɗo Buŋdi. Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, gee osiiji kaaw a ŋa gem sellen̰ ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi ho ŋa kaawtu pey a Buŋ berji satkin taat samaane. Iŋ taar-at ko, Etiyeen ooyit kaaw-ata. Iŋ taar-at ko, ŋa mattu di.
Ɗo bi ka Iisa Masi, Buŋ ƴiimiijit kaay min ɗo muuti. Ŋa bal mate asaan Buŋ ƴiimiijit pey. Ka seener gay, min ŋa Buŋ ƴiimiijit kaay-at, ŋa elgigɗo tak-tak.
Kar ya waan ginno imaan gay, gi gediraaɗo ŋaa aawe Buŋ-ak, asaan ŋa pakira kadar Buŋ goy anne ho ŋa beraag haginey ɗo ŋuur kuuk bariyaaga. Iŋ taar-at ko, gi aamin kadar ŋa goy anne ho ŋa beraag haginey ɗo ŋuur kuuk bariyaaga.
Nowe gay, iŋ imaanco, Buŋ gaariijig gamin kuuk ŋa bal tale misa gamin kuuk cigile ɗo adiy ka kiɗar. Paa ko, ŋa obtu imaanco ho ŋa siytu markaba tatiko a ŋaa jilin̰ geen̰ji ku adiy ka gerco. Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, ŋa kaawtu botol taat yaa obin̰ gee ku duniiner. Iŋ imaanco-at ko, ŋa darjiyiig Buŋ a ŋa goy sellen̰ ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi.
Min Ibraayim koliiga-ak, ŋa ictu niyine a ŋaa ɗeete ɗo wer kaak ŋaaji berin haginey. Ɗo ɗeetin̰ji-ak, ŋa ɗeettu, ŋa ibanno wer kaak ŋa ɓaayiyo.
Min ŋaar-ak, Ibraayim aamintu ɗo Buŋdi. Ŋa goytu ɗo kiɗ kaak Buŋ kaawtu a ŋa ɓaawe ɗo darre-ata. Ŋa goytu goye ɗo gerdi ar tambaay iŋ Isaaka iŋ Yakuub, ŋuur oki kuuk asa goye sawa iŋ ŋaara. Ɗo darre-at ko, ŋa goytu iŋ Yakuub.
Asaan Buŋ iban kadar Buŋ meen̰ji kat pinig geeger kaak gin jamay. Ŋaar kat pinig geeger-aka ho ŋa pinig sawa.
Ɗo imaanco ko, Sawuul ooyit gudurre ta Buŋdi, ta obtu gudurre taat ŋaa wee mico. Taar sa tatik ko ote ho ta gastu gudurre taat Buŋ kaawiitit ɗo Ibraayim. Iŋ amaanne oki, ta obtu gudurre taat Buŋ kaawiitit ɗo geemir a ŋaaco kaawe a Buŋ yaa obin̰ji.
Ampaa ko, min ɗo gem rakki-ak di, ŋu weeyig wee ka marbinto. Gee ŋuur-ak ar kaalin kuuk goy kuwa ka samaaner, wal maan ka amiydi ginno min ɗo pisin̰ji di gemo.
Gee-ak okin̰co mattu ɗo imaanco, asaan ŋu bal gasin̰ gamin kuuk Buŋ kaawtu a ŋaaco kaawe ɗo geemir a ŋuu obin̰co. Kar gay, ŋu ooyit kaawoy, ŋu ooyiita ho ŋu osiicot kaawco ɗo geemir a ŋu martaw ho martico di.
Ka seener, ya ŋu kaawa pa-ak, ŋu gaara kadar ŋu bariya botol taat ŋuu gine darre ta meen̰co.
Ya ɗo menaw ŋuur-ak di, ŋu pakira min ɗo darre taat ŋu amiltu min ɗo darre-ata, wal ŋuu rasin̰ pey wiktin ta ŋuu yeepe.
Kar diŋ gay, ŋuur coor kurumbiin-aŋ nec ko mat ko ka gusuurdi. Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, Buŋ balco gase botol taat ŋuu kolin̰co, asaan ŋaar siy ko geeger kaak ŋa doɓtu.
Wiktin taat Buŋ geciig Ibraayim iŋ Isaaka, Buŋ geciig gecin̰ji. Ibraayim ŋaar kaak gas gaanuun kaak Buŋ kaawtu a ŋaaji bere gaayo, ŋa ooytu satkine. Paa ko, ŋa giniit riy taar-at ar taar-ata.
Ŋaar ko kaak Buŋ kaawiiji ɗo Ibraayim aman: " Ɗo bi ka Isaaka ko, siŋji yaa kolin̰ baaco. "
Ɗo tan̰ji-at, ŋa pakirtu a Buŋ gin gudurre ya ŋa nooyin̰ ŋaar oki min ɗo muuti. Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, Iisa deliiji daŋla aman:
Min Isaaka doriit kaaw-at, ŋa ooyiico ɗo koogin ku Yakuub iŋ Ezaayi ho ŋa barkiyiigu.
Min Yakuub mattu, iŋ imaanco ko, ŋa barkiyiig koogin ku Yuusup okin̰co ho ŋa dersitu ɗo uŋji ka maginer.
Wiktin taat Yuusup gaastu iŋ imaanco, ŋa moyiit kaaw taat gee ku Israyeel yaa amile min ɗo darre-ata. Iŋ imaanco ko, ŋa moyiit kaaw taat ŋa kaawiico ɗo sooniikar ho ŋa kaawiico ɗo bi ka geen̰ji ku Israyeel a ŋuu ɗeete.
Min ŋu weeyig Muusa, aginiyji cigiliiga nam koɗok subba min ŋu weeyig ween̰ji. Ŋu bal gine kolaw asaan ŋu tal mic-ak samaane. Iŋ taar-at oki, ŋu bal gine kolaw ɗo kaaw ta sultinniidi.
Muusa gay, iŋ imaanco, min ŋa mattu, ŋa pooctu a ŋuu kolin̰ roŋ ka rom ta Parawon.
Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, ŋa kaawtu pey a ŋaa coone gee ku Buŋdi a ŋuu gase saamiye ka zunuubinnico sooɗ di. Ɗo bi ŋaar-ak ko, gee kuuk aamin-ak yaa gase saamiye ka zunuubinnico sooɗa.
Uudin taat ŋa rakiy n̰epe markab kapak-ak, ŋa ɓaawtu dakina ɗo gee ku Meser a ŋaa gasin̰ malle ka samaaner. Ŋa tala kar maan kaak yaaji ase misa iŋ kapak-aka, asaan ŋa tala kar maan kaak ŋaa kappiyen̰ji.
Ɗo bi ka imaanco ko, Sultan Meser rasig goyin̰ji. Ŋa bal gine kolaw ɗo sultan asaan ŋa gedarro obin̰ji paa di. Sando, sultan ŋaar gay gedarro taaɓiyin̰ji uudin taat amil kara.
Ɗo bi ka imaanco ko, Yuudinna bertu izinne a ŋuu gine iidin ta *Paakdi ho ŋuu koocin̰ baar ku hadinner, paa kat, tatkaw ka Yuudinnar toɗtu dapin̰ko yaa min̰e awalle min ɗo aginiyco ku awalle.
Ka kawtinti, ŋu aaliig markaba kaak ŋu koliy barre kaak ŋu koliy barre kaak ŋu koliy barre kaak ŋu koliy barre kaak ŋu koliy barre kaak ŋu koliy barre kaak ŋu koliy barre kaak ŋu koliy barre kaak ŋu koliy barre kaak ŋu koliy barre kaak ŋu koliy barre kaak ŋu koliy barre kaak goy ɗatik amiydi. Hiyya, gee ku Meser sooɗtu nam ŋu deeyiigu.
Ɗo wiktin taar-at, gee kuuk gooƴaag geeger ka Zeriiko, ansi-ak, ŋu un̰jitu ya ŋu ɗooɗin̰ pey menaw peesira. Min gee-ak doriit kaaw-at, ŋu iban kadar durdurre-at yaa eeze.
Ɗo bi ka imaanco, Akaab taat ob daatko-at bal ooye iŋ gee kuuk pooc aamine. Kar taar gay ŋa ooytu iŋ aapiye ɗo een̰ji kuuk gooƴaag Zeruzaleem iŋ aapiye.
Ya nu kaaw gay, maa di naaji kaawe pey? Wiktin taat nu kaawtu biŋkico ɗo bi ka Gedeon, Baraak, Samiyeel, Iisa, Dawuud, Samiyeel, iŋ nabiinna okin̰co, wiktin taat nu siirtu-an gaaye, wiktin taar-at yaa nece misa.
Gee-ak, iŋ imaanco, ŋu berco sultaninna ku Buŋdi a ŋuu goye sellen̰ ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi. Ŋu giniy gamin kuuk sellen̰ ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi. Ŋu gaartu gaare Kabarre ta Gala, ŋu gediriico gaare biŋkico ku geemir.
Ŋu gaasit gudurrey ta aki, ŋu gaɗtu min ɗo aki, ŋu gaɗtu min ɗo *seepinpan, ŋu gaɗtu min ɗo raɗuwniico, ŋu gaɗtu gudurrico iŋ gudurrey, ŋu ɓaawtu sellen̰ ɗo bi ka askirnar, ŋu ɓaawtu sellen̰ ɗo uŋji ka Buŋdi ho ŋu ɓaawtu awalle gee ku pey.
